{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "破晓之龙约 剑之觉醒",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "那是300年前的故事——憧憬广阔世界的\\n阿尔贝琉斯和碧龙耶梦加得一同踏上旅途。\\n然而，为了解救遭到狄涅尔帝国兵\\n袭击的女子穆穆雅娜，阿尔贝琉斯\\n拔出了她所携带的神秘之剑。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "伊莉雅与圣域龙\\n成功封印魔神后过了700年——\\n那时的格拉斯迪亚大陆\\n因长期的战乱而凋敝不堪。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "在那个混沌年代，\\n诞生了一个名为狄涅尔的国家。\\n谁也没有料到，\\n这个崇拜魔神的国家狄涅尔\\n居然唤醒了被封印的魔神。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "于是，世界再度面临\\n魔神的威胁。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "人们皆畏惧灾厄，\\n然而却有一名人类挺身而出。\\n他继承了古老契约的“龙之血”，\\n那个奇迹人物的名字就是——\\n阿尔贝琉斯。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "与魔神英勇抗争的阿尔贝琉斯\\n成为了人们的希望。\\n不同种族的伙伴\\n纷纷集结到了他的身旁。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "阿尔贝琉斯凭借众人的团结之力，\\n成功封印了魔神。\\n“第二次封魔战争”\\n至此画上了句号。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "战后，以阿尔贝琉斯\\n为中心的国家\\n在一片焦土之上渐渐兴起。\\n那便是——\\n阿尔贝里亚王国。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "打倒“邪恶”并带给人们希望的\\n英雄成为了复兴国家的王，\\n并维护着世界的秩序吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "真是个夸张的英雄故事。\\n如今被人们所传颂的“他”\\n简直是超乎常人的存在。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "但我记忆最深刻的……\\n呵呵，都是多久之前的事了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "那时我还不知道世界有多大。\\n而那家伙的理想\\n也只不过是个理想。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "那时人与龙之间，\\n尚存常理这道巨大的隔阂……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "而事到如今，\\n当时的世界反倒如梦似幻起来。\\n你不觉得吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "阿尔贝琉斯。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "300年前——",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "耶梦加得！\\n快看……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100031_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝琉斯",
            "context": "这就是把格拉斯迪亚大陆\\n划分为南北两地的雄伟山脉啊！\\n不枉我们特意来看它。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100031_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "嗯……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110387_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "这点程度的山脉还不足为奇。\\n世上应该还有很多比这里\\n更雄伟的崇山峻岭吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100031_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝琉斯",
            "context": "是吗！\\n还有比这里高得多的山啊。\\n那遍览全世界的山好像也很有趣呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110387_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "你一个人的话想去哪就去哪。\\n我现在这副身体想唤来暴风\\n都大费周章，不能一直陪着你。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100031_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝琉斯",
            "context": "哦？原来你变成人形\\n也能唤来暴风吗。\\n不过你可别在闹市区这么做啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110387_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "这我可没法答应你。\\n龙向来不干涉人类的生活……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110387_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "我之所以唤来暴风\\n不是为了带给人类利弊，\\n而是为了满足大自然的需要。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100031_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝琉斯",
            "context": "唉……\\n不管人类再怎么祈祷暴风别来，\\n其实还是看你的心情吗。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110387_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "我们只是在坚守各自的领域而已。\\n人类与龙还是不要过度\\n干预彼此比较好。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100031_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝琉斯",
            "context": "你又来了。我觉得人类与龙……\\n还是要携手共存，\\n这个世界才会更广阔",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110387_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "那你要我怎么办？按人类的需求\\n呼风唤雨吗？要是真那样做了，\\n很可能导致天下大乱。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110387_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "龙是自然的代行者，\\n同时也是秩序的维护者，\\n和人类保持距离也是为了避免纷争。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100031_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝琉斯",
            "context": "那这世界永远都不会有所改变吧。\\n虽然这样的日子很平静，\\n但也不会有进步……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100031_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝琉斯",
            "context": "嗯？镇上好吵。\\n到底发生了什么……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110386_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "啊……抱、抱歉。\\n我，那个……有急事……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100031_04",
                "110386_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "找到了！她在那！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110386_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "你这女人，我们不会再让你跑了。\\n老老实实把剑交出来的话，\\n我们就饶你一命。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110386_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "我、我不要！\\n不能把它交给你们这些\\n狄涅尔帝国的人……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "狄涅尔帝国军队长",
            "context": "是吗？那就别怪我们强抢了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110386_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100031_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝琉斯",
            "context": "虽然不清楚状况，但这也太\\n暴力了吧？既然你们说要强抢，\\n我可不能充耳不闻。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "狄涅尔帝国军队长",
            "context": "你这家伙算老几！\\n你会为多管闲事而后悔的——\\n给我除掉碍事的人！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120041_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "狄涅尔帝国兵",
            "context": "是！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100031_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝琉斯",
            "context": "没有商量的余地吗……\\n这样的话，\\n我也只能动用强硬手段了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "狄涅尔帝国军队长",
            "context": "什么！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100031_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝琉斯",
            "context": "不好意思，就凭你们几个，\\n一起上也赢不了我，\\n还是老老实实地离开吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "狄涅尔帝国军队长",
            "context": "该死的……你少得意！这就让你\\n见识一下我们狄涅尔帝国的力量！\\n伟大的主人啊，赐予我等力量吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100031_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝琉斯",
            "context": "什么！？他召唤来了魔兽！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "狄涅尔帝国军队长",
            "context": "现在吃惊还太早了！\\n就算搭上性命，也要完成\\n皇帝陛下赐予我的使命！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "狄涅尔帝国军队长",
            "context": "唔……呃……\\n呃啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110387_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "人类变成了魔兽！？\\n这种力量难道是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100031_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝琉斯",
            "context": "耶梦加得，那帮小喽啰\\n可以交给你对付吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110387_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "没办法，看来这些人\\n是扰乱世间常理的存在，\\n身为龙无法坐视不管。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100031_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝琉斯",
            "context": "交给你了，耶梦加得。\\n我就负责……对付这个家伙！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120031_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "狄涅尔帝国军队长",
            "context": "吾之性命，属于……狄涅尔……\\n咕噢噢噢噢噢！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100031_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝琉斯",
            "context": "可恶！好强的力量！\\n这样下去的话……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120031_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "狄涅尔帝国军队长",
            "context": "咕噢噢噢噢噢！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100031_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝琉斯",
            "context": "剑……断了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120031_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "狄涅尔帝国军队长",
            "context": "咕噢噢噢噢噢！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100031_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝琉斯",
            "context": "哇啊啊啊！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120031_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "狄涅尔帝国军队长",
            "context": "咕……吾之……使命……\\n扫除吾主复活的障碍！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100031_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝琉斯",
            "context": "不好！他朝她那边去了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110386_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "呀啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100031_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝琉斯",
            "context": "喂，你没事吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110386_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "嗯，我……没事……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100031_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝琉斯",
            "context": "别勉强自己。\\n你正中了那头怪物的攻击，\\n暂时还是不要动比较好。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110386_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "但、但是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100031_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝琉斯",
            "context": "别担心，我还没精明到\\n会丢下你逃跑。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110386_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "……\\n不……你还是快逃吧……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100031_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝琉斯",
            "context": "什么？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110386_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "你别管我了，快点逃走吧。\\n只是，我有一事相求。\\n这把剑——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110386_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "圣剑“龙约”，能请你帮忙\\n送到伊莉雅教的大圣堂吗！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110386_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "这把剑有可能\\n关乎整个世界的命运！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100031_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝琉斯",
            "context": "把这么重要的东西……\\n交给一个萍水相逢的男人\\n真的好吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110386_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "我不能让它被敌人夺走……\\n而且你看起来值得信任。\\n所以，拜托你了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100031_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝琉斯",
            "context": "这样啊……\\n既然你如此信任我，\\n还有一个办法。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0066",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110386_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "诶？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0067",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100031_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝琉斯",
            "context": "我来用这把剑\\n迎战那头怪物。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0068",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110386_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "不、不可以……\\n这把剑是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0069",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120031_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "狄涅尔帝国军队长",
            "context": "唔噢噢噢……使命……使命……\\n使命！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0070",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100031_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝琉斯",
            "context": "抱歉，现在没时间商量了！\\n先借我一用！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0071",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110386_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "不是的！\\n这把剑是拔不出来的。\\n所以还是别……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0072",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120031_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "狄涅尔帝国军队长",
            "context": "咕啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0073",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120031_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝琉斯",
            "context": "唔噢噢噢噢噢！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0074",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120031_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "狄涅尔帝国军队长",
            "context": "呃啊啊啊啊啊啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0075",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100031_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝琉斯",
            "context": "发、发生什么了？\\n我打败了魔兽……不……\\n是消灭了它们？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0076",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100031_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝琉斯",
            "context": "刚……刚才到底是怎么回事？\\n出鞘的瞬间，剑光一闪，\\n魔兽眨眼间就……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0077",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110386_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "怎么可能……\\n没想到会在这种地方遇到。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0078",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110386_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "你就是……\\n你就是龙之血的继承者！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20431_01_0079",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}